name: Sad Statue of Liberty
description:
This painting would depict a Chinese dragon breathing fire onto New York City, with the Statue of Liberty in the foreground, still standing tall against the flames, right after dropping the torch with a look of sadness on her face, her copper skin tarnished and her robes in tatters. The dragon would be shown in all its ferocious glory, steadily stepping as it sets the city ablaze. The painting would be full of intense chaos, the cityscape is in shambles, with smoke and fire rising from buildings and debris littering the streets.

Dimensions: 3072x4096 Pixels

Tools used: GLIDE, image editor, SwinIR, GPT3
